sExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2526372\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2526372\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Apr 26, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104ccf1665702761572.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ccf1665702761572.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ccf1665702761572.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ccf1665702761572\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">throw \n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"ccf1665702761572__throw_244558\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Throw an exception.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"ccf1665702761572__topic_d78263e1_d78264e1_d78265e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ccf1665702761572__p_d78266e1_d78267e1_d78268e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">throw</span>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">ErrorNumber</var> {<code class=\"ph codeph\">,</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Description</var> {<code class=\"ph codeph\">,</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">AdditionalInformation</var>} }</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ccf1665702761572__p_d78269e1_d78270e1_d78271e1\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">throw -10050, \"No privilege to access Customer information\", \"USERID=%%(ID.USER);USERNAME=%%(NAME.USER)\"</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ccf1665702761572__topic_d51472e1_d51473e1_d51474e1_d51475e1_d51476e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1007961e88\">Parameters</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"ccf1665702761572__table_d7631e1_d7632e1_d7633e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ccf1665702761572__table_d7631e1_d7632e1_d7633e1__entry__1\">\n Parameter\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ccf1665702761572__table_d7631e1_d7632e1_d7633e1__entry__2\">\n Data Type\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ccf1665702761572__table_d7631e1_d7632e1_d7633e1__entry__3\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ccf1665702761572__table_d7631e1_d7632e1_d7633e1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">ErrorNumber</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ccf1665702761572__table_d7631e1_d7632e1_d7633e1__entry__2\">\n Numeric\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ccf1665702761572__table_d7631e1_d7632e1_d7633e1__entry__3\"> The error number. Positive numbers are thrown\n                        as negative numbers. <code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code> is thrown as <code class=\"ph codeph\">-1\n                           &lt;UGENERR_ERROR&gt;</code>. <p class=\"p\">To avoid confusion, use numbers\n                           outside the range <code class=\"ph codeph\">-1</code> though <code class=\"ph codeph\">-9999</code>,\n                           which are reserved for Uniface errors.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ccf1665702761572__table_d7631e1_d7632e1_d7633e1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Description</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ccf1665702761572__table_d7631e1_d7632e1_d7633e1__entry__2\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ccf1665702761572__table_d7631e1_d7632e1_d7633e1__entry__3\"> A brief, mnemonic-like description. \n                     </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ccf1665702761572__table_d7631e1_d7632e1_d7633e1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">AdditionalInformation</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ccf1665702761572__table_d7631e1_d7632e1_d7633e1__entry__2\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ccf1665702761572__table_d7631e1_d7632e1_d7633e1__entry__3\"> More detailed information about the error. \n                     </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ccf1665702761572__topic_d51477e1_d51478e1_d51479e1_d51480e1_d51481e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1007961e184\">Return Values</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ccf1665702761572__p_d78278e1_d78279e1_d78280e1\">After the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">throw</span> statement, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> has the value that was specified in the <var class=\"keyword varname\">ErrorNumber</var> argument, and <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerrorcontext</span> has items with IDs <code class=\"ph codeph\">DESCRIPTION</code> and <code class=\"ph codeph\">ADDITIONAL</code>, which have the values of the <var class=\"keyword varname\">Description</var> and <var class=\"keyword varname\">AdditionalInformation</var> arguments respectively.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ccf1665702761572__p_d78281e1_d78282e1_d78283e1\">If <var class=\"keyword varname\">Description</var> is omitted, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerrorcontext</span> will have a <code class=\"ph codeph\">DESCRIPTION</code> item with the value <code class=\"ph codeph\">Custom exception</code>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ccf1665702761572__p_d78284e1_d78285e1_d78286e1\">If <var class=\"keyword varname\">AdditionalInformation</var> is omitted, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerrorcontext</span> will have no <code class=\"ph codeph\">ADDITIONAL</code> item.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ccf1665702761572__topic_d51482e1_d51483e1_d51484e1_d51485e1_d51486e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1007961e245\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ccf1665702761572__d5916e20\">Allowed in all component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ccf1665702761572__topic_d51487e1_d51488e1_d51489e1_d51490e1_d51491e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1007961e255\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ccf1665702761572__p_d78296e1_d78297e1_d78298e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">throw</span> statement enables you to throw a custom exception without affecting system exceptions, so that you can use the exception bubble to handle custom errors.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ccf1665702761572__p_d78299e1_d78300e1_d78301e1\">Error numbers are always negative numbers, so the provided <var class=\"keyword varname\">ErrorNumber</var> should be a negative number. If it is a positive number, the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">throw</span> statement will throw it as a negative number. If the provided <var class=\"keyword varname\">ErrorNumber</var> is zero, the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">throw</span> statement will throw error <code class=\"ph codeph\">-1 &lt;UGENERR_ERROR&gt;</code>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ccf1665702761572__p_d78302e1_d78303e1_d78304e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">throw</span> statement stops execution of the current block of code. If it is located:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ccf1665702761572__li_d33320e1_d33321e1_d33322e1\">Inside a <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">try...catch...endtry</span> block, code execution continues in one of the associated <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">catch</span> blocks, if there is an applicable one. If not, the exception bubbles up to the next <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">try</span>-level or to the caller of the module.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ccf1665702761572__li_d33323e1_d33324e1_d33325e1\">Outside a <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">try...catch...endtry</span> block but in a ProcScript module that has the <code class=\"ph codeph\">throws</code> clause, code execution continues within the calling module, with the statement following the call to this module.\n </li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ccf1665702761572__p_d78305e1_d78306e1_d78307e1\">For example:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">public operation loadOrder\nthrows\nparams\n string pOrderId : IN\nendparams\n if (pOrderId == \"\")\n throw -10001, \"Invalid input parameter\", \"PARAM_INDEX=1;PARAM_NAME=pOrderId;EXPECTED_VALUE=Not NULL\"\n endif\n ID.ORDER/init = pOrderId\n retrieve/e \"ORDER\"\nend\ntry\n retrieve\n throw -10054, \"Description\", \"more context list\"\ncatch -2, -4, -10054\n ; code to handle the expected exceptions\nendtry\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526372\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526372\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "throw Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Apr 26, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 throw Throw an exception. throw ErrorNumber { , Description { , AdditionalInformation } } Example: throw -10050, \"No privilege to access Customer information\", \"USERID=%%(ID.USER);USERNAME=%%(NAME.USER)\" Parameters Parameter Data Type Description ErrorNumber Numeric The error number. Positive numbers are thrown as negative numbers. 0 is thrown as -1 <UGENERR_ERROR> . To avoid confusion, use numbers outside the range -1 though -9999 , which are reserved for Uniface errors. Description String A brief, mnemonic-like description. AdditionalInformation String More detailed information about the error. Return Values After the throw statement, $procerror has the value that was specified in the ErrorNumber argument, and $procerrorcontext has items with IDs DESCRIPTION and ADDITIONAL , which have the values of the Description and AdditionalInformation arguments respectively. If Description is omitted, $procerrorcontext will have a DESCRIPTION item with the value Custom exception . If AdditionalInformation is omitted, $procerrorcontext will have no ADDITIONAL item. Use Allowed in all component types. Description The throw statement enables you to throw a custom exception without affecting system exceptions, so that you can use the exception bubble to handle custom errors. Error numbers are always negative numbers, so the provided ErrorNumber should be a negative number. If it is a positive number, the throw statement will throw it as a negative number. If the provided ErrorNumber is zero, the throw statement will throw error -1 <UGENERR_ERROR> . The throw statement stops execution of the current block of code. If it is located: Inside a try...catch...endtry block, code execution continues in one of the associated catch blocks, if there is an applicable one. If not, the exception bubbles up to the next try -level or to the caller of the module. Outside a try...catch...endtry block but in a ProcScript module that has the throws clause, code execution continues within the calling module, with the statement following the call to this module. For example: public operation loadOrder throws params string pOrderId : IN endparams if (pOrderId == \"\") throw -10001, \"Invalid input parameter\", \"PARAM_INDEX=1;PARAM_NAME=pOrderId;EXPECTED_VALUE=Not NULL\" endif ID.ORDER/init = pOrderId retrieve/e \"ORDER\" end try retrieve throw -10054, \"Description\", \"more context list\" catch -2, -4, -10054 ; code to handle the expected exceptions endtry Copy Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}